<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>e</ex>r</expan> pfleger, als ir uns
                                                nehst und yecz <expan>verschr<ex>iben</ex></expan>
                                                habt von C. Keinspeken
                                                <expan>weg<ex>en</ex></expan>, der in
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> fenknuss ligt etc.,
                                                das <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> wir wol
                                                  <expan>vernom<ex>en</ex></expan> und
                                                  <expan>lass<ex>en</ex></expan> ewr
                                                  <expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan>
<expan>wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz
                                                  <expan>ders<ex>elb</ex></expan> Keinspeck und
                                                etlich <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>vo<ex>n</ex></expan> der
                                                  <expan>Leynb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan>
<expan>eine<ex>n</ex></expan>
<expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>armma<ex>n</ex></expan> auch von der
                                                  <expan>Leynb<ex>ur</ex>g</expan> eins nachts in
                                                  <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>r</expan> stat so hart
                                                gewundt und <expan>geslag<ex>en</ex></expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz er mer
                                                  <expan>zu<ex>m</ex></expan> tod genaigt was denn
                                                zum <expan>lebe<ex>n</ex></expan>; darauf
                                                  <expan>dess<ex>elben</ex></expan>
<expan>wunde<ex>n</ex></expan> frewnd an uns
                                                  <expan>begerte<ex>n</ex></expan>, die an
                                                  <expan>sölich<ex>er</ex></expan> geschicht
                                                schuldig <expan>w<ex>er</ex>en</expan> zu
                                                  <expan>halte<ex>n</ex></expan>; und also ist noch
                                                kein gancze eygenschaft wie sich des
                                                  <expan>wunde<ex>n</ex></expan> sach
                                                  <expan>mache<ex>n</ex></expan> mag. Denn wo wir
                                                  <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>erberk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb
                                                  <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                                                  <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut
                                                  <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
